anh Minh song kiếm. Sau nhiều lần nghi ngờ, Thẩm Vân nhìn thấy Trương Chi Lâm đã xả thân cứu giúp, hai người trân trọng nhau, cuối cùng đã thành công sử dụng song kiếm, đánh bại U Hoàng!</p>","tmdb":{"type":"movie","id":"1005168","season":null,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"modified":"2022-09-11T12:14:25.000Z","cast":["Trần Hạo Dân","Từ Đông Đông","Xiong Xinxin","Zhang Mingming","Lương Tiểu Long","Yu Yao","Wang Yuman"],"director":["Kenyeung"],"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trần Hạo Dân","name_vi":"Trần Hạo Dân","name_original":"Benny Chan Ho-Man","tmdb_id":1314817,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cGNOprzxJntHcg6db0HZOdyCZX8.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1314817"},{"name":"Từ Đông Đông","name_vi":"Từ Đông Đông","name_original":"Xu Dongdong","tmdb_id":1822751,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nV1wWx7nzt8kOdvoNNWDdCZEUsl.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1822751"},{"name":"Xiong Xinxin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Xiong Xinxin","tmdb_id":131732,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cpJikUtykWmK02h5m9gYEzUuYui.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/131732"},{"name":"Zhang Mingming","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhang Mingming","tmdb_id":2811001,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/vzsbPOCL4flFpe4cSgjrwxZIIEe.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2811001"},{"name":"Lương Tiểu Long","name_vi":"Lương Tiểu Long","name_original":"Bruce Leung Siu-Lung","tmdb_id":83491,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/thgf1TvGZu8Zmpd2enLaPWsqcXb.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/83491"},{"name":"Yu Yao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yu Yao","tmdb_id":3093593,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5HLEPBEtXcNe5uvSm8ac51e5y8U.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3093593"},{"name":"Wang Yuman","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Wang Yuman","tmdb_id":2696501,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/tOzNOIsXI06NgLo7Wtdz3vYPnBp.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themov